[
    {
        "text": "Hi.",
        "start": 0.329,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm Rebecca from engVid.",
        "start": 1.329,
        "duration": 1.441
    },
    {
        "text": "Today I'm especially excited to welcome you to a new series that I've created called:",
        "start": 2.77,
        "duration": 4.799
    },
    {
        "text": "\"How to Speak like a Manager\".",
        "start": 7.569,
        "duration": 3.001
    },
    {
        "text": "In this series you will learn how to take general English and upgrade it to business",
        "start": 10.57,
        "duration": 5.969
    },
    {
        "text": "English.",
        "start": 16.539,
        "duration": 1.011
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 17.55,
        "duration": 1.01
    },
    {
        "text": "And we'll be doing that by looking at different verbs that you can use, adjectives, nouns,",
        "start": 18.56,
        "duration": 5.129
    },
    {
        "text": "and so on.",
        "start": 23.689,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 24.689,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "But today in this lesson we will be focusing on eight verbs.",
        "start": 25.689,
        "duration": 3.981
    },
    {
        "text": "But you might be asking: \"Only eight verbs and I can become a manager?\"",
        "start": 29.67,
        "duration": 5.08
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, yes.",
        "start": 34.75,
        "duration": 1.94
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Why?\"",
        "start": 36.69,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Because I'm going to show you how these eight verbs, to start with, can actually be used",
        "start": 37.69,
        "duration": 5.31
    },
    {
        "text": "in hundreds of ways, in different collocations or combinations of words, so therefore you'll",
        "start": 43.0,
        "duration": 7.2
    },
    {
        "text": "be able to use them in all kinds of situations.",
        "start": 50.2,
        "duration": 3.37
    },
    {
        "text": "Definitely in professional situations, but also in social situations or personal situations.",
        "start": 53.57,
        "duration": 6.8
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 60.37,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, let's start right now.",
        "start": 61.37,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 63.67,
        "duration": 1.3
    },
    {
        "text": "So let's suppose what you want to say in general English or regular English is something like",
        "start": 64.97,
        "duration": 6.58
    },
    {
        "text": "this: \"I need to find out what's wrong.\"",
        "start": 71.55,
        "duration": 4.25
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 75.8,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, on this side is all the regular English or the general English.",
        "start": 76.8,
        "duration": 3.56
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 80.36,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "And on this side we're going to express the same idea, but in higher English, in more",
        "start": 81.36,
        "duration": 5.37
    },
    {
        "text": "advanced business English or more professional English.",
        "start": 86.73,
        "duration": 3.19
    },
    {
        "text": "And you're going to help me because I didn't write the word in yet.",
        "start": 89.92,
        "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
        "text": "You're going to help me because perhaps you already know some of these words, but even",
        "start": 93.12,
        "duration": 4.41
    },
    {
        "text": "if you know them you might not realize how many different ways we can actually use those",
        "start": 97.53,
        "duration": 5.31
    },
    {
        "text": "same words, and that's what I want you to be able to do.",
        "start": 102.84,
        "duration": 3.41
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 106.25,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So suppose your idea in your mind is that: \"I need to find out what's wrong.\"",
        "start": 107.25,
        "duration": 5.31
    },
    {
        "text": "So how can we say that in more professional English?",
        "start": 112.56,
        "duration": 3.32
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I need to\", the verb starts with \"i\": \"I need to _______ the problem.",
        "start": 115.88,
        "duration": 7.87
    },
    {
        "text": "I need to identify the problem.\"",
        "start": 123.75,
        "duration": 8.98
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 132.73,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, our first word today is \"identify\".",
        "start": 133.73,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "Say it after me: \"identify the problem\".",
        "start": 136.55,
        "duration": 3.83
    },
    {
        "text": "Good.",
        "start": 140.38,
        "duration": 1.01
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, suppose the idea you're trying to convey is: \"I need to fix the problem.\"",
        "start": 141.39,
        "duration": 6.56
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 147.95,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Fix\" is a very ordinary word, so what better word could we use here?",
        "start": 148.95,
        "duration": 4.31
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I need to _______ the issue or the issues.",
        "start": 153.26,
        "duration": 4.49
    },
    {
        "text": "I need to\", you might know this word.",
        "start": 157.75,
        "duration": 5.19
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I need to resolve\", okay?",
        "start": 162.94,
        "duration": 4.21
    },
    {
        "text": "So, \"resolve\" is just like \"solve\", but usually we say: \"Solve the problem\", but we might",
        "start": 167.15,
        "duration": 6.17
    },
    {
        "text": "say: \"Resolve the issue\".",
        "start": 173.32,
        "duration": 1.57
    },
    {
        "text": "And \"resolve\" is an even higher, more advanced word.",
        "start": 174.89,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "And the higher vocabulary that you use, the more professional you will sound.",
        "start": 178.33,
        "duration": 4.69
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 183.02,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "And that's what our goal is.",
        "start": 184.02,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Right?",
        "start": 185.02,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, next: \"I need to give people confidence.\"",
        "start": 186.02,
        "duration": 4.52
    },
    {
        "text": "So what's a good word or verb for that?",
        "start": 190.54,
        "duration": 3.09
    },
    {
        "text": "\"To give somebody confidence\" is to, something starts with \"m\": \"I need to _______ my employees.",
        "start": 193.63,
        "duration": 6.8
    },
    {
        "text": "I need to...\"",
        "start": 200.43,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you know this word?",
        "start": 202.09,
        "duration": 1.229
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm sure you've heard it.",
        "start": 203.319,
        "duration": 3.481
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Motivate\".",
        "start": 206.8,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 208.96,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Say it after me: \"Motivate\" or \"motivate\".",
        "start": 211.12,
        "duration": 4.47
    },
    {
        "text": "You can say the \"t\"; sometimes it's easier and clearer for people to understand you when",
        "start": 215.59,
        "duration": 5.259
    },
    {
        "text": "you say the \"t\".",
        "start": 220.849,
        "duration": 1.461
    },
    {
        "text": "So let's say the \"t\" now: \"Motivate.",
        "start": 222.31,
        "duration": 2.47
    },
    {
        "text": "I need to motivate my employees\" or: \"I need to motivate my employees.\"",
        "start": 224.78,
        "duration": 6.11
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 230.89,
        "duration": 1.1
    },
    {
        "text": "Instead of saying: \"I need to give people confidence\", because you see that all the",
        "start": 231.99,
        "duration": 3.859
    },
    {
        "text": "verbs here are very ordinary, everyday verbs, and those are higher-level verbs.",
        "start": 235.849,
        "duration": 5.901
    },
    {
        "text": "Next: \"I need to give clients my attention.\"",
        "start": 241.75,
        "duration": 4.15
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, we have a very weak verb here, so how can you say that: \"I need to give my attention",
        "start": 245.9,
        "duration": 8.94
    },
    {
        "text": "to my clients or give clients my attention\"?",
        "start": 254.84,
        "duration": 3.259
    },
    {
        "text": "The word...",
        "start": 258.099,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "The verb starts with \"f\": \"I need to _______ on our clients.\"",
        "start": 259.099,
        "duration": 5.03
    },
    {
        "text": "What's the verb?",
        "start": 264.129,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you know it?",
        "start": 265.129,
        "duration": 2.07
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I need to focus\", okay?",
        "start": 267.199,
        "duration": 4.61
    },
    {
        "text": "Say it after me: \"Focus\".",
        "start": 271.809,
        "duration": 2.25
    },
    {
        "text": "Be careful how you pronounce this word because otherwise it can sound improper.",
        "start": 274.059,
        "duration": 3.58
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 277.639,
        "duration": 1.261
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I need to focus on our clients.\"",
        "start": 278.9,
        "duration": 3.379
    },
    {
        "text": "Sounds a lot better than saying: \"I need to give my attention to my clients.\"",
        "start": 282.279,
        "duration": 3.931
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 286.21,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I need to focus\".",
        "start": 287.21,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Next: \"I need to spend as little as possible\".",
        "start": 288.21,
        "duration": 4.519
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Spend as little\" means spend as little money.",
        "start": 292.729,
        "duration": 3.81
    },
    {
        "text": "So what's one word that captures that idea, to spend as little as possible?",
        "start": 296.539,
        "duration": 5.711
    },
    {
        "text": "It starts with \"m\": \"I need to _______ our expenses or our costs.\"",
        "start": 302.25,
        "duration": 7.4
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you know what it is?",
        "start": 309.65,
        "duration": 5.62
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 315.27,
        "duration": 5.2
    },
    {
        "text": "So the word is \"minimize\".",
        "start": 320.47,
        "duration": 2.419
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 322.889,
        "duration": 1.511
    },
    {
        "text": "I've written it twice because this is the American way with a \"z\" or a \"z\", and this",
        "start": 324.4,
        "duration": 5.681
    },
    {
        "text": "is the British spelling with a \"s\"; both are correct.",
        "start": 330.081,
        "duration": 3.708
    },
    {
        "text": "So: \"I need to minimize our expenses.\"",
        "start": 333.789,
        "duration": 3.62
    },
    {
        "text": "When you minimize something, you reduce it to as much as possible.",
        "start": 337.409,
        "duration": 5.37
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 342.779,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Minimize\".",
        "start": 343.779,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "And, again, we're going to see so many different ways in which we can use this verb and all",
        "start": 344.779,
        "duration": 4.741
    },
    {
        "text": "of these verbs.",
        "start": 349.52,
        "duration": 1.099
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 350.619,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Not just the way I've done it here with \"resolve the issues\".",
        "start": 351.619,
        "duration": 2.431
    },
    {
        "text": "We're going to see lots of other things you can resolve or lots of other things you can",
        "start": 354.05,
        "duration": 4.339
    },
    {
        "text": "minimize.",
        "start": 358.389,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 359.389,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Next: \"I need to make as much money as possible.\"",
        "start": 360.389,
        "duration": 4.381
    },
    {
        "text": "Don't we all?",
        "start": 364.77,
        "duration": 1.019
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 365.789,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, what's a good verb for that?",
        "start": 366.789,
        "duration": 2.741
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, something that starts with \"m\": \"I need to _______ our earnings\".",
        "start": 369.53,
        "duration": 5.21
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Earnings\" means the money that you make.",
        "start": 374.74,
        "duration": 3.25
    },
    {
        "text": "So what's the verb?",
        "start": 377.99,
        "duration": 2.13
    },
    {
        "text": "It's very similar to \"minimize\"...",
        "start": 380.12,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "It's actually the opposite of \"minimize\", it is...",
        "start": 382.3,
        "duration": 4.19
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah, I can hear some of you.",
        "start": 386.49,
        "duration": 3.079
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Maximize\", good.",
        "start": 389.569,
        "duration": 2.581
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 392.15,
        "duration": 1.289
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, I'm going to write it with the \"z\" or the \"z\", but you can also write it with",
        "start": 393.439,
        "duration": 5.57
    },
    {
        "text": "an \"s\" and it's correct.",
        "start": 399.009,
        "duration": 1.791
    },
    {
        "text": "What you need to do regarding that British and American spelling is stay consistent.",
        "start": 400.8,
        "duration": 4.88
    },
    {
        "text": "If you're using American spelling, then use American spelling; if you're using British",
        "start": 405.68,
        "duration": 4.12
    },
    {
        "text": "spelling, use British.",
        "start": 409.8,
        "duration": 1.609
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 411.409,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Try to stay consistent.",
        "start": 412.409,
        "duration": 1.111
    },
    {
        "text": "Next: \"I need to get more work.\"",
        "start": 413.52,
        "duration": 4.289
    },
    {
        "text": "We're not making enough money.",
        "start": 417.809,
        "duration": 1.341
    },
    {
        "text": "We need more work.",
        "start": 419.15,
        "duration": 1.689
    },
    {
        "text": "So instead of saying: \"Get more work\", we can say: \"_______ more business\".",
        "start": 420.839,
        "duration": 6.3
    },
    {
        "text": "What's that really good verb here?",
        "start": 427.139,
        "duration": 2.55
    },
    {
        "text": "It starts with \"g\": \"generate\".",
        "start": 429.689,
        "duration": 3.72
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 433.409,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Generate more business\" means to make, create...",
        "start": 434.939,
        "duration": 6.94
    },
    {
        "text": "Create more business.",
        "start": 441.879,
        "duration": 1.47
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 443.349,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Instead of just saying: \"Get more work\", which sounds very ordinary: \"We need to generate",
        "start": 444.349,
        "duration": 4.77
    },
    {
        "text": "more business.",
        "start": 449.119,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "We need to create more business.\"",
        "start": 450.119,
        "duration": 1.98
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 452.099,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "And the last one: \"I need to use the new ideas.\"",
        "start": 453.099,
        "duration": 3.88
    },
    {
        "text": "So, instead of saying \"use\", there is a verb that starts with \"i\" which means to put something",
        "start": 456.979,
        "duration": 6.5
    },
    {
        "text": "into practice, to use it: \"I need to _______ the strategies\" or \"I need to _______ the",
        "start": 463.479,
        "duration": 8.44
    },
    {
        "text": "recommendations.\"",
        "start": 471.919,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you know that word?",
        "start": 472.919,
        "duration": 2.881
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 475.8,
        "duration": 1.799
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Implement\".",
        "start": 477.599,
        "duration": 1.81
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 479.409,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "\"To implement an idea\" means to put it into practice.",
        "start": 481.209,
        "duration": 6.04
    },
    {
        "text": "So let's say you have an idea.",
        "start": 487.249,
        "duration": 1.371
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 488.62,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "That's great, we all have good ideas, but what are you going to do with that idea?",
        "start": 489.62,
        "duration": 3.43
    },
    {
        "text": "You want to use it, you want to put it into practice, you want to implement it.",
        "start": 493.05,
        "duration": 5.19
    },
    {
        "text": "But not only can you implement ideas, you can implement lots of other things which we're",
        "start": 498.24,
        "duration": 5.329
    },
    {
        "text": "going to talk about as we continue the lesson, but here we're talking about implementing",
        "start": 503.569,
        "duration": 4.811
    },
    {
        "text": "a strategy, which is a plan.",
        "start": 508.38,
        "duration": 2.769
    },
    {
        "text": "So, repeat after me now, just get used to saying these things out loud.",
        "start": 511.149,
        "duration": 5.151
    },
    {
        "text": "The more you say them, the more comfortable you will be saying them, and the more likely",
        "start": 516.3,
        "duration": 4.57
    },
    {
        "text": "you are to actually use them at work, or in a job interview, or something...",
        "start": 520.87,
        "duration": 4.59
    },
    {
        "text": "Or in your emails, your professional emails.",
        "start": 525.46,
        "duration": 2.49
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 527.95,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Just get comfortable with them.",
        "start": 528.95,
        "duration": 1.49
    },
    {
        "text": "Are you ready?",
        "start": 530.44,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Identify the problem\", \"resolve the issues\", \"motivate my employees\", \"focus on our clients\",",
        "start": 531.82,
        "duration": 16.25
    },
    {
        "text": "\"minimize our expenses\", \"maximize our earnings\", \"generate more business\", and \"implement the",
        "start": 548.07,
        "duration": 15.0
    },
    {
        "text": "strategies\".",
        "start": 563.07,
        "duration": 1.04
    },
    {
        "text": "Good.",
        "start": 564.11,
        "duration": 1.03
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 565.14,
        "duration": 1.04
    },
    {
        "text": "Now I'm going to show you how to take these eight words and use them in so many other",
        "start": 566.18,
        "duration": 4.81
    },
    {
        "text": "ways.",
        "start": 570.99,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "I'll be right back.",
        "start": 571.99,
        "duration": 1.04
    },
    {
        "text": "All right, so let's start with our first four words.",
        "start": 573.03,
        "duration": 3.95
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 576.98,
        "duration": 1.31
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Identify\", \"resolve\", \"motivate\", and \"generate\".",
        "start": 578.29,
        "duration": 4.92
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 583.21,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "So let's look at how many different ways we can use these words, and these are just a",
        "start": 584.65,
        "duration": 5.05
    },
    {
        "text": "few of them.",
        "start": 589.7,
        "duration": 1.51
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 591.21,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "I've actually created for you a resource which has more than 100 words which you can use",
        "start": 592.21,
        "duration": 7.37
    },
    {
        "text": "in combination with just these eight verbs.",
        "start": 599.58,
        "duration": 3.03
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 602.61,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So afterwards I'll tell you where you can download that from, from our website.",
        "start": 603.61,
        "duration": 3.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 607.39,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "But now let's look at some of the possibilities, how we can use these words.",
        "start": 608.39,
        "duration": 3.77
    },
    {
        "text": "So, the first word: \"identify\", so again: What does \"identify\" mean?",
        "start": 612.16,
        "duration": 4.92
    },
    {
        "text": "It means to find who or what.",
        "start": 617.08,
        "duration": 3.46
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 620.54,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "For example: If you want to start a new business, you need to also identify the risks of starting",
        "start": 621.54,
        "duration": 7.66
    },
    {
        "text": "a new business.",
        "start": 629.2,
        "duration": 1.3
    },
    {
        "text": "What is \"the risk\"?",
        "start": 630.5,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "The danger.",
        "start": 631.62,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 632.62,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "The possible problems, the risks.",
        "start": 633.62,
        "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
        "text": "Or if you want to hire someone, you need to identify or find, you need to identify the",
        "start": 636.14,
        "duration": 6.42
    },
    {
        "text": "right person for the job.",
        "start": 642.56,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "Right?",
        "start": 644.74,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Good.",
        "start": 645.74,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "That's part of a manager's role, to recruit good people.",
        "start": 646.74,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 649.47,
        "duration": 1.4
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, what I want to show you on this side is that you can not only use these verbs in",
        "start": 650.87,
        "duration": 5.85
    },
    {
        "text": "business and professional situations, but also in all kinds of other situations in your",
        "start": 656.72,
        "duration": 5.29
    },
    {
        "text": "life.",
        "start": 662.01,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "For example: You and your spouse might sit down and discuss the fact that we need to",
        "start": 663.01,
        "duration": 7.96
    },
    {
        "text": "identify the reasons why Johnny's not doing well in school, and how we can help him.",
        "start": 670.97,
        "duration": 6.17
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 677.14,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"We need to identify the ways in which we can save money.\"",
        "start": 678.14,
        "duration": 3.9
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 682.04,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So you see that we can use it in everyday life as well, but we're using higher-level",
        "start": 683.04,
        "duration": 4.96
    },
    {
        "text": "vocabulary.",
        "start": 688.0,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 689.0,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Now: \"resolve\".",
        "start": 690.0,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, \"resolve\" is like solve.",
        "start": 691.2,
        "duration": 2.35
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 693.55,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So: \"We need to resolve the situation\", \"We need to resolve a crisis\".",
        "start": 694.55,
        "duration": 6.84
    },
    {
        "text": "What's \"a crisis\"?",
        "start": 701.39,
        "duration": 1.49
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a very serious situation.",
        "start": 702.88,
        "duration": 1.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 704.66,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Very bad, emergency kind of situation is a crisis.",
        "start": 705.66,
        "duration": 3.99
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 709.65,
        "duration": 1.42
    },
    {
        "text": "\"We need to resolve the disagreements between our children because they keep fighting.\"",
        "start": 711.07,
        "duration": 5.29
    },
    {
        "text": "Or: \"We need to resolve the tension between these two neighbours.\"",
        "start": 716.36,
        "duration": 6.59
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 722.95,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Tension\" is like stress.",
        "start": 723.95,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 726.13,
        "duration": 1.57
    },
    {
        "text": "Next word: \"motivate\".",
        "start": 727.7,
        "duration": 1.09
    },
    {
        "text": "Right?",
        "start": 728.79,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"We need to motivate our staff\", \"We need to motivate the team to do well.\"",
        "start": 729.79,
        "duration": 5.05
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 734.84,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"We need to motivate our kids\".",
        "start": 735.84,
        "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Kids\" is like slang for children.",
        "start": 737.72,
        "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Motivate our kids to do their homework\", \"I need to motivate my spouse to find another",
        "start": 739.84,
        "duration": 7.17
    },
    {
        "text": "job\".",
        "start": 747.01,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Spouse\", what does this word mean?",
        "start": 748.01,
        "duration": 1.93
    },
    {
        "text": "Husband or wife.",
        "start": 749.94,
        "duration": 2.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 752.44,
        "duration": 1.69
    },
    {
        "text": "And now the word \"generate\".",
        "start": 754.13,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 755.89,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So what is \"generate\"?",
        "start": 756.89,
        "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
        "text": "To create more of something.",
        "start": 757.91,
        "duration": 1.83
    },
    {
        "text": "So: \"To generate more sales\", of course that's usually the objective and the goal of most",
        "start": 759.74,
        "duration": 6.0
    },
    {
        "text": "companies, or to generate more revenue.",
        "start": 765.74,
        "duration": 2.95
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Revenue\" is just a business word for basically more money.",
        "start": 768.69,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 772.53,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 773.53,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Or: \"You need to generate more interest in a particular subject.\"",
        "start": 774.53,
        "duration": 4.33
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's say your child is not interested in math or in some other subject, or geography,",
        "start": 778.86,
        "duration": 5.42
    },
    {
        "text": "and you want to generate...",
        "start": 784.28,
        "duration": 1.09
    },
    {
        "text": "You want to be able to help him to generate more interest in that subject or generate",
        "start": 785.37,
        "duration": 5.35
    },
    {
        "text": "more enthusiasm for helping you in the house.",
        "start": 790.72,
        "duration": 3.55
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 794.27,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Things like that.",
        "start": 795.27,
        "duration": 1.47
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, as I said, we can use all kinds of subjects-okay?-for...",
        "start": 796.74,
        "duration": 6.16
    },
    {
        "text": "In our sentence.",
        "start": 802.9,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "We can say: \"We need to\".",
        "start": 803.9,
        "duration": 2.25
    },
    {
        "text": "You can talk about your company, we can say: \"The company needs to...\"",
        "start": 806.15,
        "duration": 4.78
    },
    {
        "text": "You could talk about your government, you can say: \"The government needs to\", whatever.",
        "start": 810.93,
        "duration": 5.38
    },
    {
        "text": "Or: \"My children need to\", \"My neighbours need to\", \"My brother needs to\", \"My friend",
        "start": 816.31,
        "duration": 5.31
    },
    {
        "text": "needs to\", \"I need to\".",
        "start": 821.62,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 823.3,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 824.3,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "And not only \"need to\" before all these verbs; you can say: \"I need to identify the risks\",",
        "start": 825.3,
        "duration": 6.49
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I should resolve this situation\", \"I must motivate the staff\", or \"I have to generate",
        "start": 831.79,
        "duration": 6.59
    },
    {
        "text": "more sales\".",
        "start": 838.38,
        "duration": 1.13
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 839.51,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So you see that you can use all kinds of verbs here as well.",
        "start": 840.51,
        "duration": 3.37
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 843.88,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, when I come back we'll look at the other four verbs that we learned.",
        "start": 844.88,
        "duration": 4.86
    },
    {
        "text": "Now let's focus on our next four words.",
        "start": 849.74,
        "duration": 2.55
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 852.29,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "And they are: \"focus\", \"minimize\", \"maximize\", and \"implement\".",
        "start": 853.29,
        "duration": 7.31
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 860.6,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's look at how we can use these words.",
        "start": 861.6,
        "duration": 2.69
    },
    {
        "text": "You can focus on your priorities.",
        "start": 864.29,
        "duration": 3.61
    },
    {
        "text": "What are \"priorities\"?",
        "start": 867.9,
        "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
        "text": "The things that are most important, the things you should really be paying attention to are",
        "start": 868.92,
        "duration": 5.69
    },
    {
        "text": "your priorities.",
        "start": 874.61,
        "duration": 1.23
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 875.84,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's say you have five things to do in a day, but the first thing is the most important",
        "start": 876.84,
        "duration": 4.45
    },
    {
        "text": "thing, that's your most important priority, so you should focus on that priority.",
        "start": 881.29,
        "duration": 6.04
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 887.33,
        "duration": 1.3
    },
    {
        "text": "Or you can focus on your goals, your objectives, your dreams, your visions, your ambitions,",
        "start": 888.63,
        "duration": 7.13
    },
    {
        "text": "and so on.",
        "start": 895.76,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 896.88,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, we can use these words in any sphere of life, also your academic life.",
        "start": 897.88,
        "duration": 6.02
    },
    {
        "text": "You can...",
        "start": 903.9,
        "duration": 1.19
    },
    {
        "text": "Perhaps you need to focus on your studies, you need to focus on improving your grades.",
        "start": 905.09,
        "duration": 5.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 910.33,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Or improving your health.",
        "start": 911.33,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 913.13,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "You can also add a word in there, like I did just now: \"Focus on improving my health\",",
        "start": 914.13,
        "duration": 6.77
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Focus on increasing my grades\", okay?",
        "start": 920.9,
        "duration": 3.71
    },
    {
        "text": "Things like that.",
        "start": 924.61,
        "duration": 1.15
    },
    {
        "text": "Next: \"minimize\".",
        "start": 925.76,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, \"minimize\" means to reduce to the lowest level, so: \"We need to minimize costs\".",
        "start": 927.29,
        "duration": 6.14
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Costs\" are like expenses.",
        "start": 933.43,
        "duration": 2.78
    },
    {
        "text": "\"We need to minimize the time that's wasted by many people in this department.\"",
        "start": 936.21,
        "duration": 6.58
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 942.79,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"We need to minimize the noise-all right?-that's sometimes in this neighbourhood.\"",
        "start": 943.79,
        "duration": 5.92
    },
    {
        "text": "And: \"We need to minimize the amount of money we are spending on coffee.\"",
        "start": 949.71,
        "duration": 4.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 954.49,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Apparently I forgot to write that.",
        "start": 955.49,
        "duration": 1.7
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay, never mind.",
        "start": 957.19,
        "duration": 1.37
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 958.56,
        "duration": 1.219
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Maximize\".",
        "start": 959.779,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, \"maximize\" means to make as high as possible.",
        "start": 960.779,
        "duration": 4.331
    },
    {
        "text": "This was to make as low as possible; \"maximize\" is to make as high as possible.",
        "start": 965.11,
        "duration": 4.62
    },
    {
        "text": "So: \"We need to maximize our profit.\"",
        "start": 969.73,
        "duration": 2.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 972.51,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Profit\" is the money that you earn after you have paid everything and everyone.",
        "start": 973.51,
        "duration": 5.95
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 979.46,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Need to maximize efficiency\".",
        "start": 980.46,
        "duration": 2.39
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Efficiency\" is productivity, how...",
        "start": 982.85,
        "duration": 5.239
    },
    {
        "text": "How well you work in terms of time, in terms of all your resources.",
        "start": 988.089,
        "duration": 4.651
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Maximize efficiency\".",
        "start": 992.74,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 995.2,
        "duration": 1.23
    },
    {
        "text": "As a student or as a parent, you want your children or you want yourself to...",
        "start": 996.43,
        "duration": 4.95
    },
    {
        "text": "You want to be able to maximize your grades.",
        "start": 1001.38,
        "duration": 3.16
    },
    {
        "text": "You want to maximize your investments.",
        "start": 1004.54,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "If you put money into a particular stock or share, you want to make sure that the investment",
        "start": 1007.3,
        "duration": 5.74
    },
    {
        "text": "is maximized.",
        "start": 1013.04,
        "duration": 1.35
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 1014.39,
        "duration": 1.14
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, here you see that I am using a lot of other business vocabulary and generally more",
        "start": 1015.53,
        "duration": 5.95
    },
    {
        "text": "advanced vocabulary, so you have a chance as you learn these eight verbs to also learn",
        "start": 1021.48,
        "duration": 6.02
    },
    {
        "text": "a lot of these collocations and combinations with other nouns.",
        "start": 1027.5,
        "duration": 5.689
    },
    {
        "text": "And in case you're not familiar with what those mean, then that's an opportunity to",
        "start": 1033.189,
        "duration": 4.161
    },
    {
        "text": "go even further with this lesson.",
        "start": 1037.35,
        "duration": 2.26
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 1039.61,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 1040.61,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "The last verb: \"implement\".",
        "start": 1041.61,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, \"to implement something\" means to actually put it into practice, not just talk about",
        "start": 1042.61,
        "duration": 6.0
    },
    {
        "text": "it, but to actually do it.",
        "start": 1048.61,
        "duration": 1.4
    },
    {
        "text": "So: \"We need to implement the changes\", \"We need to implement the new policies that the",
        "start": 1050.01,
        "duration": 6.749
    },
    {
        "text": "department or that the company has come up with\", \"We need to implement the safety rules\",",
        "start": 1056.759,
        "duration": 7.491
    },
    {
        "text": "or \"We need to implement the consultant's suggestions or recommendations\", or anything",
        "start": 1064.25,
        "duration": 6.409
    },
    {
        "text": "like that.",
        "start": 1070.659,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 1071.659,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, again, on that resource which I've created, you will see hundreds of examples of how you",
        "start": 1072.659,
        "duration": 6.14
    },
    {
        "text": "can use just these eight words.",
        "start": 1078.799,
        "duration": 1.97
    },
    {
        "text": "And in future lessons you'll see more verbs and more examples, so this is a really quick",
        "start": 1080.769,
        "duration": 6.811
    },
    {
        "text": "shortcut.",
        "start": 1087.58,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 1088.58,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "This is a vocabulary hack, actually, for you.",
        "start": 1089.58,
        "duration": 3.319
    },
    {
        "text": "And a hack is a shortcut, a way for you to expand your vocabulary more quickly and more",
        "start": 1092.899,
        "duration": 5.171
    },
    {
        "text": "easily.",
        "start": 1098.07,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 1099.07,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, what I suggest that you do now is a few things.",
        "start": 1100.07,
        "duration": 3.54
    },
    {
        "text": "So, first go to our website at www.engvid.com, and there you can do a quiz on these eight",
        "start": 1103.61,
        "duration": 8.769
    },
    {
        "text": "words-okay?-to make sure that you really know the meaning, understand how to use them and",
        "start": 1112.379,
        "duration": 5.341
    },
    {
        "text": "so on.",
        "start": 1117.72,
        "duration": 1.01
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 1118.73,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Next, you can...",
        "start": 1119.73,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "While you're at the website you can also download for free the resource that I've created on",
        "start": 1120.89,
        "duration": 4.93
    },
    {
        "text": "how to use these eight words with many other word combinations.",
        "start": 1125.82,
        "duration": 5.01
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 1130.83,
        "duration": 1.54
    },
    {
        "text": "Then if you really want to start implementing the recommendations that I've made to you,",
        "start": 1132.37,
        "duration": 8.49
    },
    {
        "text": "then write a sentence, write one sentence, write two, write three - choose one word and",
        "start": 1140.86,
        "duration": 5.13
    },
    {
        "text": "write a sentence in the comments section of our engVid website, or on our Facebook, or",
        "start": 1145.99,
        "duration": 6.01
    },
    {
        "text": "somewhere-okay?-or on YouTube.",
        "start": 1152.0,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "So, write a comment using one, or two, or three of these words.",
        "start": 1154.4,
        "duration": 5.109
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 1159.509,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Try to really make those words your own.",
        "start": 1160.509,
        "duration": 2.701
    },
    {
        "text": "And you could write...",
        "start": 1163.21,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "You could say, like: \"I need to maximize my income.\"",
        "start": 1164.21,
        "duration": 5.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 1169.37,
        "duration": 1.519
    },
    {
